rust-proxmox-sdn-types (0.2.3-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * sdn: ospf: host the NetworkType enum (Broadcast, NonBroadcast,
    PointToPoint, PointToMultipoint) so proxmox-frr and proxmox-ve-config can
    share it without ve-config pulling in the optional `frr` feature.

  * sdn: rename the `area` module to `ospf` since it now hosts more
    OSPF-specific types than just Area.

 -- Proxmox Support Team <support@proxmox.com>  Fri, 15 May 2026 03:39:40 +0200

